361
00:19:40,956 --> 00:19:41,956
(You know,)

362
00:19:42,797 --> 00:19:44,997
(I never was a religious person.)

363
00:19:45,837 --> 00:19:47,317
(I never made wishes.)

364
00:19:50,396 --> 00:19:51,757
