474
00:27:49,837 --> 00:27:51,357
unless you want to die.

475
00:28:00,196 --> 00:28:01,037
Lady Gu!

476
00:28:01,476 --> 00:28:02,436
Lady Gu!

477
00:28:19,117 --> 00:28:19,876
Your Majesty.

478
00:28:21,557 --> 00:28:23,037
