514
00:29:34,117 --> 00:29:35,117
If the crown prince

515
00:29:35,317 --> 00:29:37,317
hands over the command seal

516
00:29:37,436 --> 00:29:38,956
instead of charging in,

517
00:29:39,117 --> 00:29:40,236
